<%- include("../../partials/header") %>

<div class="jumbotron-fluid" id="jumbotronRoadBikes">
   <img src="" alt="">
    <div id="roadBikesHeaderText">
        <h1 class="display-4">Track/Urban Bikes</h1>
        <p class="lead">Craftsmanship and passion are at the heart of Cinelli</p>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div id="borderHeaderBottom">
     <ul> 
        <li class="bottomBorderColors" id="red"></li>
        <li class="bottomBorderColors" id="yellow"></li>
        <li class="bottomBorderColors" id="black"></li>
        <li class="bottomBorderColors" id="green"></li>
    </ul>
  </div>
  <div id="bikesAboutText">
    <p>Lorem Ipsum is simply dummy text of the printing and typesetting industry. Lorem Ipsum has been the industry's standard dummy text ever since the 1500s, when an unknown printer took a galley of type and scrambled it to make a type specimen book.</p>
